(634, '<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family:''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">每年两度的房交会历来被视为长沙楼市风向标，</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">5</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">29</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">日下午，以</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">魅力长沙，宜居城市</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">为主题的湖南长沙第</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">31</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">届房交会闭幕。据组委会统计，房交会</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">天累计成交各类房屋</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">238</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">套，成交面积</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3.6</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">万㎡，成交金额</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2.18</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿元，观展市民达</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">26</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">万余人次，</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">VIP</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">登记超过</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">1.58</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">万套。本届房交会在展示目前长沙房地产开发全貌的同时，也为调控背景下未来楼市的走势提供了一个审视的机会。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image002.jpg" /></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">房交会关键词一：<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">展览</b></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">本届房交会的一大亮点在于商品房市场中众多纯新盘，</span><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://floor.0731fdc.com/cinfo.php?id=13211" target="_blank"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; text-underline: none"><span lang="EN-US">华远</span></span><span style="color: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none"><font face="Times New Roman">&middot;</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; text-underline: none"><span lang="EN-US">华中心</span></span></a></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://floor.0731fdc.com/cinfos.php?id=15632" target="_blank"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; text-underline: none"><span lang="EN-US">澳海澜庭</span></span></a></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://floor.0731fdc.com/cinfos.php?id=13151" target="_blank"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; text-underline: none"><span lang="EN-US">恒广</span></span><span style="color: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none"><font face="Times New Roman">&middot;</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; text-underline: none"><span lang="EN-US">国际景园</span></span></a></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://floor.0731fdc.com/cinfos.php?id=14773" target="_blank"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; text-underline: none"><span lang="EN-US">高林仕家</span></span></a></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://floor.0731fdc.com/cinfos.php?id=11429" target="_blank"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; text-underline: none"><span lang="EN-US">昆仑和府</span></span><span style="color: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none"><font face="Times New Roman">&middot;</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; text-underline: none"><span lang="EN-US">华庭</span></span></a></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://floor.0731fdc.com/cinfo.php?id=15492" target="_blank"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; text-underline: none"><span lang="EN-US">新天地中心</span></span></a></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><a href="http://floor.0731fdc.com/cinfo.php?id=15232" target="_blank"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; text-underline: none"><span lang="EN-US">锦泰东环国际</span></span></a></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">等项目一起新鲜亮相房交会。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 11.25pt"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">中海会</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">恒广会</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">澳海会</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">象屿会</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;&hellip;&hellip;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">记者在房交会现场观察到，多家参展楼盘在房交会期间并没有实际房源推出，名目繁多的免费入会充斥在整个会展当中。如果说去年秋季房交会交易与展览仍保持在一个微妙的平衡，那么今年春交会已完全打破这个平衡。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">11</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年开年随着&ldquo;国八条&rdquo;等一系列政策出台，市场正经历政策出台后的适应期。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">4~5</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月的成交量并没有出现如往年的快速上扬，所以本届房交会出现展多于销的情况也在情理之中。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 11.25pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 11.25pt; text-align: center"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image004.jpg" /></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 11.25pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-indent: 11.25pt"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">据粗略统计，本届长沙房交会参展的</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">46</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个项目中，近九成为预售楼盘，多为开盘在即而借此平台展示形象和积蓄客户，现场在售项目微乎其微，而在售项目中，又以尾盘居多。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">客观地说，本届参展楼盘多为预售楼盘，现场可卖房源不多，是本届房交会总体相对平坦的主要原因之一。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> </font></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">关键词二：<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal">买方</b></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font size="3"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;&ldquo;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">购房者也越来越有主见，提的问题也越来越细致专业，不仅涉及地段、户型、周边配套、按揭政策等基本因素，还会了解楼盘品质、开发商口碑、周边项目情况乃至未来城市规划。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&rdquo;</font><a href="http://floor.0731fdc.com/cinfo.php?id=13091" target="_blank"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: windowtext; font-family: 宋体; text-decoration: none; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; text-underline: none"><span lang="EN-US">橄榄君庭</span></span></a></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">项目置业顾问李小姐在房交会期间切身感受到了购房群体更加理性。</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">&ldquo;</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">房交会现场我们特意准备了看房专车，很多客户还必须到现场实地看过房子，家里人商量过后才会最终下单。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image006.jpg" /><br clear="all" style="mso-ignore: vglayout" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">在政策出台后，随着观望情绪复燃与交易量下滑。大市场不可避免的进入买方市场状态，购房者在此时渐渐掌握市场主导权。但是，在地产交易中买方市场的状态是相对的、也是受政策影响而且受刚性需求推动而短期的。在买方市场的情况下，各楼盘之间的竞争将达到最大化。随后几个月之中各个楼盘之间的状态以及购房者与各个营销团队之间的状态绝对不会如房交会上体现的如此平静。波澜不惊的表面实则暗潮汹涌，市场的走向受调控力度的影响将越来越严重。同样是上半年政策密集出台的</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年下半年市场火爆，但却不能作为今年对市场预判的基准。实际上，</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">10</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年下半年及年尾的消费井喷以及使得市场的消费能力大幅度消耗，消费市场需要一段时间进行适应。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image008.jpg" /></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">长沙住宅产品鉴赏：</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3"><img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image010.jpg" /></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">江山帝景</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">91</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">㎡（</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">2+1</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">两房房）</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">布局方正，赠送面积较大两房产品中较少见的大开间客厅。拥有三房气质的两房</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image012.jpg" /></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">江山帝景</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">116,</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">三房两厅两卫</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">空间利用率高，功能性完善</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">多个阳台与飘窗设置，赠送面积大</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">此次房交会回到长沙，第一感觉就是赠送面积大的&ldquo;</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">N+1</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&rdquo;住宅在长沙发展迅速。大部分房型都通过飘窗与空间花园的设置来加大赠送面积，提高产品的性价比。一方面体现了二线城市地产项目的竞争激烈化，另一方面也显现出市场购买力随着价格的上扬而倾向于总价上有优惠的大赠送面积住宅。在市场状况好的时候，买卖双方也存在一定程度上的妥协。而性价比高的&ldquo;</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">N+1</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&rdquo;产品也将逐渐走进常德。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image014.jpg" /></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">松雅湖金岸</span><font face="Times New Roman"> <span lang="EN-US">85.67</span></font><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">㎡</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">两房</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">赠送区域多</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">南北通透，多向采光</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">这个户型基本上是&ldquo;</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">N+1</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">&rdquo;产品的一个赠送面积最大化的样本了。如图所示在</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">80</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">多平米的空间中占了约</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">3/1</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">的地方都属于半赠送。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image016.jpg" /></font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">宜居莱茵城</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> 88</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">㎡两房</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">空间分布均匀，浪费面积少</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">多向采光，赠送面积大</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">在长沙，市内五区的土地资源越来越稀缺。所以点式产品为了在节约空间的同时保证居住的舒适性越来越多的应用到了阶梯式排列与多向采光的应用。应该庆幸的是，在常德目前还能方便的找到一梯两户的板式产品。但是在不久的将来，户均资源占比高的板式住宅将随着土地稀缺性的升高而越来越少见。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image018.jpg" /></font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">宜居莱茵城</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> 100</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">㎡三房</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">南北通透，功能齐全</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">排布规整，面积使用率非常高</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">长沙的两房与三房产品面积通常在</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">75~110</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">之间，相比于目前常德两房</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">90~100</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，三房</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">110~130</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">的现状要缩水不少。而常德市场的消费习惯正是</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">06~07</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年时候长沙市场的翻版，随着价格走高而消费力提升的速度捉襟见肘。所以在几年之后，或许从今年开始常德的商品房住宅在面积定位上将开始&ldquo;瘦身&rdquo;。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image020.jpg" /></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">宜居莱茵城</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> 130</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">㎡三房</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">功能齐全，主卧功能齐全</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">南北通透，动静分区明显</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">虽然市场上紧凑型讲究性价比的产品所占比重越来越高，但是也不乏追求舒适性的板式产品。住宅始终是用于居住的实用型商品，而人们追求优质生活的脚步一直在前进。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image022.jpg" />&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">瑞都豪庭</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> 91.2</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">㎡</span><font face="Times New Roman"> </font><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">两房</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">布局紧凑，空间利用率高</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">南北通透，赠送面积很大</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">瑞都华庭的户型上不仅标识了赠送面积的范围，更是给出了装修与改进建议。空中花园的利用是的原本的阳光两房变成了紧凑型三房。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image024.jpg" />&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">长房时代城</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> 88</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">㎡</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> 2+1</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">两房</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">方正空间，赠送面积很大</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">空间排布严谨是长沙市场上住宅产品的通用特点，如上图所示的</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman">88</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">㎡两房，虽然餐厅的设置稍显拥挤，但是整体布局的规整让人感觉心旷神怡。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image026.jpg" /></font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">长房时代城</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> 158</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">㎡四房</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">市场上比较少见的四房，把中大户型的气势演绎得很到位。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">虽然四房产品在市场上占比不断减少，但是从居住舒适性而言确实是两房与三房产品所不能比的。动静分区明显与功能性完备是大户型产品的共通优点。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image028.jpg" /></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">美丽新世界</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> 101</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">㎡三房</span></font><span lang="EN-US"><br style="mso-special-character: line-break" />\r\n<br style="mso-special-character: line-break" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">紧凑型三房，南北通透多向采光</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">点式产品通过空间排列重组，也能部分拥有板式产品南北通透的优点。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3"><img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image028.jpg" />&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">英祥春天</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> 82</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">㎡两房</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">紧凑三房，多向采光。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">南北通透，大赠送面积。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image030.jpg" /></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><font size="3"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">英祥春天</span><span lang="EN-US"><font face="Times New Roman"> 83</font></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">㎡两房</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">紧凑型两房，大赠送面积</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">多向采光，空间利用率高</font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image032.jpg" />&nbsp;<img alt="" src="/upload/2011/6/2/image034.jpg" /></font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><v:shape id="_x0000_s1030" type="#_x0000_t75" style="margin-top: 7.8pt; z-index: 5; left: 0px; margin-left: 243pt; width: 212.65pt; position: absolute; height: 280.8pt; text-align: left"><font size="3"><font face="Times New Roman"><v:imagedata o:title="金色家园128" src="file:///C:DOCUME~1ADMINI~1LOCALS~1Tempmsohtml1\02clip_image031.jpg"></v:imagedata><w:wrap type="square"></w:wrap></font></font></v:shape></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: left"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><font size="3">在常德，南北通透的板式产品渐渐也增加有非常可观的赠送面积。例如上图所示火车站大市场开发建设有限公司旗下&ldquo;金色家园&rdquo;项目中的主力户型。虽然不如长沙的房子紧凑，但是在空间布局以及宜居与功能性并重的设计理念上在市场同类产品中表现非常突出。两房与三房通过赠送面积抵消公摊面积，实现&ldquo;零公摊&rdquo;商品房住宅。虽然个别项目不能代表整体市场，但是提升性价比和优化户型设计来满足购买力日渐缩水的市场肯定是常德地产项目今后几年的发展趋势。</font></span></p>', 0, 0, 0, '', 0, 1, '', '', ''),
(635, '<p><strong><span style="font-family: Arial">2011年6月2日&mdash;6月10日，汀湘湖畔举办端午感恩回馈活动，为客户送上三重惊喜：</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>一重惊喜：凡活动期间到汀湘湖畔成功购房的外地客户，均可报销往返路费3000元整；<br />\r\n二重惊喜：凡活动期间到汀湘湖畔看房的客户，均可获得一份精美的端午龙粽；<br />\r\n三重惊喜：活动期间，汀湘湖畔所有的业主均可到售楼部领取一份感恩端午龙粽。</strong></p>\r\n<p>柳叶湖畔，90&mdash;133㎡实景现房，买就多得一间房。0736&mdash;8808088<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 0, 0, 0, '', 0, 1, '', '', '');
