(636, '<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><font face="Times New Roman">常房通<span lang="EN-US">[2011]14</span>号<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 方正小标宋简体; font-size: 22pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 16pt"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">各县市区房地产管理局、房地产开发企业：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">为加强商品房销售管理，维护消费者合法权益，促进房地产市场健康发展，根据《城市房地产开发经营管理条例》、《商品房销售管理办法》、《城市商品房预售管理办法》、《国务院办公厅关于促进房地产市场平稳健康发展的通知》（国办发〔<span lang="EN-US">2010</span>〕<span lang="EN-US">4</span>号）、《国务院关于坚决遏制部分城市房价过快上涨的通知》（国发〔<span lang="EN-US">2010</span>〕<span lang="EN-US">10</span>号）精神，现将规范商品房销售现场公示内容的有关事项通知如下：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">一、</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">商品房销售现场公示应当遵循准确、真实、合法原<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">则。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">二、房地产开发企业、房地产经纪机构预售商品房的，其售房现场信息公示应达到以下标准：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">（一）设立证件公示栏，公示如下证件和信息：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、《商品房预售许可证》；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、《房地产开发企业资质证书》；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、《工商营业执照》；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">4</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、经规划部门批准的项目总平面图；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">5</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、房地产开发企业委托房地产经纪机构代理销售商品房的，应公示商品房销售委托书及受委托的房地产经纪机构的《工商营业执照》和《备案证书》。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">（二）设立文件（文本）公示栏（台），明示如下文件文本信息：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、《商品房销售管理办法》；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、《城市商品房预售管理办法》；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、《常德市商品房买卖合同》示范文本；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">4</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、《前期物业管理合同》；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">5</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、《业主临时管理规约》。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">（三）设立可售房源信息公示栏，公示如下信息：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、批准预售当期和原有的可售房源总套数，建筑总面积、平均销售价格（按建筑面积计算）；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、每套商品房的建筑面积（套内建筑面积、公摊面积均应标明）；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、每套房屋的销售总价和单价；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">4</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、优惠折扣及享受优惠折扣的条件；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">5</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、销售地下停车位的，应标明每个在售车位的销售价格；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">6</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、前期物业管理企业名称、物业服务内容、服务标准及收费标准。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">（四）设立其他信息公示栏，公示如下信息：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、楼盘的建筑结构，装修状况以及水、电、燃气、通讯、有线电视等基础设施配套情况；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、物业管理用房和业主公共活动用房（会所）的位置和面积；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、重要配套设施情况；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">4</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、项目可否提供银行贷款和住房公积金贷款，办理住房抵押贷款的银行和公积金管理中心的咨询电话；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">5</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、商品房所有权登记代收代办的收费项目、收费标准，代收代办费应当标明由消费者自愿选择；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">6</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">、房地产市场监督管理部门和价格主管部门的监督举报电话。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">（五）分类公示栏应设置在销售现场显著位置，因内容<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="right" style="text-align: right; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 16.0pt">&mdash;<span lang="EN-US">3</span>&mdash;</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">数量原因不便以栏目形式公示的，可印制单行本供购房人查阅。要提高公示栏的布置水平，做到明了、美观，有条件的可以利用镜框、电子屏及电脑查询系统等多种形式，公示时间为项目房屋销售结束止。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">三、各县市区房地产主管部门在办理商品房预售许可证<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">时应要求房地产开发企业将上述情况进行公示并查验，合格者方可发放预售许可证，要对销售过程中的情况进行检查，发现房地产开发企业和房地产经纪机构在销售现场未执行以上规定的，要及时通知其整改，整改合格后方能继续销售，逾期不整改的暂停网签，并作为不良经营行为记入信用档案，违反有关法律法规的，由相关部门按照有关法律法规的规定处理。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="right" style="text-align: right; text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 16pt 0pt 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">二○一一年五月十七日<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font size="3" face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font size="3" face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font size="3" face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family:''Times New Roman''">主题词：</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt">城乡建设　房地产<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>管理　通知</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 16pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0"><v:line id="_x0000_s1027" to="414pt,31.2pt" from="0,31.2pt" style="z-index: 251658240; position: absolute; text-align: left; left: 0px"></v:line><v:line id="_x0000_s1026" to="414pt,0" from="0,0" style="z-index: 251657216; position: absolute; text-align: left; left: 0px"></v:line><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">常德市房地产管理局<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><st1:chsdate year="2011" month="5" w:st="on" day="17" islunardate="False" isrocdate="False">2011<span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">年5</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">月17</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">日</span></span></st1:chsdate><span lang="EN-US">印发<o:p></o:p></span></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, 0, 0, '', 0, 1, '', '', ''),
(637, '<p style="text-align: center"><img alt="" width="550" height="366" src="/upload/2011/5/19/20114219024229.jpg" /><br />\r\n中影&bull;大时代影城外景</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5月18日晚，在中影&bull;大时代影城典雅大堂，中影集团及合作伙伴、省、市各大媒体、全市电影爱好者齐集一堂，共同见证了中影&bull;大时代影城的扬帆起航。</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><img alt="" width="550" height="366" src="/upload/2011/5/19/20114219024253.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 中影&bull;大时代影城是由中影集团联手常德市大时代影城有限公司为了带给常德市民与全球影迷相同的观影体验，共同以国际电影行业五星级标准、由资深顶级影院专业人士设计，耗资千万精心打造。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 影城大堂采用5星级酒店标准设计, 融入海洋水世界主题概念, 配合售票厅及小卖部S型一体设计线条流畅优美，带您穿越海底登陆黄金岛探险之旅。影城采用全球最先进、最专业的全数字设备，美国科视品牌2K放映机及蒙太奇服务器、美国全自动红外发射3D观影眼镜组合、7.1声道杜比技术及超视野壁式清晰全金属银幕，可放映3D大片的国际级影院，完美梦幻3D光影世界精细呈现于您面前，让您的感官体验从未有过的震撼视听刺激！</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><img alt="" width="550" height="366" src="/upload/2011/5/19/20114319024321.jpg" /><br />\r\n中影&bull;大时代影城过道</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><img alt="" width="550" height="366" src="/upload/2011/5/19/20114419024400.jpg" /><br />\r\n中影&bull;大时代影城大堂</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 影城坐落于交通便利的洞庭大道旁的芙蓉家园3楼，毗邻芙蓉王烟厂区、芙蓉大酒店、湖南文理学院等。总面积4500平方米，附设海量免费停车场。共设各具特色7个观影厅，以及一个重金打造、贵宾专有之超豪华休憩区并独享美轮美奂舒适典雅的VIP观影厅，共上千个专业豪华影厅坐席恭候您的莅临。<br />\r\n<span style="color: #ff0000">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 抢票热线:7373333<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 咨询QQ: 1106752141</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 0, 0, 0, '', 0, 1, '', '', ''),
(638, '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 常德新闻网4月30日讯（记者 胡丹）昨日，记者从市物价局了解到，从今年5月1日起，全市范围内实行一房一价，商品房经营者不得在标价之外加价销售商品房，不得收取任何未予标明的费用。省物价局近日发布《湖南省商品房销售明码标价规定实施细则》的通知(以下简称《细则》)，对此作了明确规定。同时，已销售的房源，商品房经营者应当予以明确标示。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 《细则》中所称明码标价，是指商品房经营者在销售商品房时按照《细则》的要求公开标示商品房价格、相关收费以及影响商品房价格的因素等有关情况的行为。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我省境内的房地产开发企业和中介服务机构(以下统称商品房经营者)销售新建商品房和二手商品房，都应当实行明码标价。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 《细则》规定，商品房销售明码标价实行一套一标。商品房经营者应当对每套商品房进行明码标价。按照建筑面积或者套内建筑面积计价的，还应当标示建筑面积单价或者套内建筑面积单价。对取得预售许可或者办理现房销售备案的房地产开发项目，商品房经营者要在公开销售新建商品房24小时前一次性公开全部销售房源，并严格按照申报价格明码标价对外销售。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 商品房经营者在广告宣传中涉及的价格信息，必须真实、准确、严谨。商品房经营者不得使用虚假或者不规范的价格标示误导购房者，不得利用虚假或者使人误解的标价方式进行价格欺诈。商品房销售价格有优惠折扣的，应当在标示牌的特别提示栏内明示优惠折扣及享受优惠折扣的条件。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 省物价局规定，商品房经营者应当在商品房交易场所的醒目位置，采取悬挂或放置标价牌、价目表的方式明码标价；有条件的可同时采取价格手册、电子信息屏、多媒体终端或电脑查询等方式明码标价。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 物价部门表示，商品房经营者不按照《细则》明码标价和公示收费，或者利用标价形式和价格手段进行价格欺诈的，由县级以上各级人民政府价格主管部门依据国家相关法律、法规和规章实施行政处罚。</p>', 0, 0, 0, '', 0, 1, '', '', ''),
(639, '<p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;继2011年3月26日首批百万级街铺开盘即售罄后，5月8日位于下南门核心商圈的高山街&bull;不夜城第二批商铺，情景街区-广场铺开盘10分钟即售罄，再创常德商铺现象级销售记录。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;开盘当天，高山街&bull;不夜城营销中心人头攒动，气氛热烈。的情景街区-广场铺因其特色的时尚、小资商业经营定位理念，高山街&bull;不夜城的整体规模优势，合理的投资总额，因此备受投资者的追捧。同时，当天举行的潇湘常德国际影城&ldquo;爱电影，爱生活&rdquo;的活动也吸引了众多客户及市民的眼光，最新的国内外大片电影片花欣赏，精美的卡通公仔诚意客户赠送充分体现了&ldquo;玩、乐&rdquo;的休闲概念。潇湘常德国际影城的负责人也接受了常德电视台都市频道、常德民生报、常德晚报等主流媒体的现场采访，影城预计将于暑期火爆试营业，相信届时高山街&bull;不夜城将会真正成为常德市民的全天候休闲娱乐之城。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;10分钟售罄广场铺，也让当天在座的许多没有买到铺的客户深感遗憾，目前高山街&bull;不夜城的美食天地商铺也即将发售，是实力投资者的置业首选。项目的休闲娱乐餐饮招商也在火热进行中，欢迎现场咨询。</p>\r\n<strong><span style="color: #ff0000">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 投资热线：0736-7911111</span></strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong><span style="color: #ff0000"><img width="550" height="366" alt="" src="/upload/2011/5/9/20114709104704.jpg" /></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong><span style="color: #ff0000"><img width="550" height="366" alt="" src="/upload/2011/5/9/20114709104718.jpg" /></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong><span style="color: #ff0000"><img width="550" height="366" alt="" src="/upload/2011/5/9/20114709104729.jpg" /></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><strong><span style="color: #ff0000"><img width="550" height="366" alt="" src="/upload/2011/5/9/20114709104740.jpg" /></span></strong></p>', 0, 0, 0, '', 0, 1, '', '', ''),
(640, '<p>从4月5日开始，首批VIP诚意认筹停止，同时开始春季VIP认筹。办理春季VIP认筹的客户开盘可凭认筹协议享受2000抵7000的优惠活动。</p>', 0, 0, 0, '', 0, 1, '', '', ''),
(641, '<p style="text-align: justify">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5月26日，&ldquo;金色家园&rdquo;与106.8鼎广电台联合开展&ldquo;我把热血献给党&rdquo;爱党歌曲大家唱活动。&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><img alt="" align="middle" width="700" height="525" src="http://old.cdfdc.gov.cn//upFile//2011052616071170554.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><img alt="" align="middle" width="700" height="525" src="http://old.cdfdc.gov.cn//upFile//2011052616081370554.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><img alt="" align="middle" width="700" height="525" src="http://old.cdfdc.gov.cn//upFile//2011052616090070554.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><img alt="" align="middle" width="700" height="525" src="http://old.cdfdc.gov.cn//upFile//2011052616101170554.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><img alt="" align="middle" width="700" height="525" src="http://old.cdfdc.gov.cn//upFile//2011052616110370554.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center"><img alt="" align="middle" width="700" height="525" src="http://old.cdfdc.gov.cn//upFile//2011052616115270554.jpg" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify">&nbsp;</p>', 0, 0, 0, '', 0, 1, '', '', ''),
(642, '<p><strong>城央叠墅<br />\r\n无可比拟的居住空间体验</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 清晨的第一缕阳光映进窗户，伴着中心园景淡淡的花草清香，迷人而倍感幸福。女主人推开主卧室的玻璃门，独立的阳台与更衣室，让生活更显安然与惬意。书房也就挨着主卧，那是男主人的冥想空间。次卧房的独特景观阳台，孩子的童年在此趣味发芽。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 家庭起居室位于上层中央，而特大通风明亮的会客厅，与庭院、前厅连接，让朋友间的欢声笑语从容飞扬。宽大底层双重院落花园，私家小花园是室外空间的延伸，底层半地下室多功能厅，则将家庭厅、娱乐室、工人房、储物间等完美融合，你可将它变为娱乐室、家庭影院、运动室、藏书室&hellip;&hellip;完全不受干扰的空间。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 新颖的城市叠墅，正是讲求居住功能别墅化的生活感受。<br />\r\n<strong>尊崇户型<br />\r\n已然成为奢藏的艺术品</strong><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 独有的高得房率，私家露台和空中别院的超大赠送面积，绝不仅仅是和远&bull;公园世家备受赞扬的唯一理由。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 稀缺板式大宅，大气方正，超大面宽南向客厅，罕见的双面采光主卧与翰墨书香中的阳光书房，270&deg;大景观阳台纵览天地，流露豪门气质与贵族优雅。尽管不同的建筑形态，决定了尺度的开阔与精致，但丝毫不影响私享花园的悠然度，在花园里，或培育花草，或品茶闲谈，享受阳光清风，惬意生活。将尘世的纷扰，恬然拭去。将餐厅延伸向生活露台，视野开阔，室外景观扑面而来，增添就餐情趣，当一家人其乐融融享受美餐时，仿佛置身与青山绿水之间，可谓真正私属阳光餐厅。客厅与餐厅，扩展室内空间，每层露台设置，沐浴阳光，亲情自在。<br />\r\n<strong>城央叠墅，人生刚刚好<br />\r\n</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 拥有世界级荣誉最多的不在别处。居于白马湖边的和远&bull;公园世家已为人向往，但若得城央叠墅居住体验更将生活推向极致。生命，正是一份心境，人到不惑刚刚好。人生，往前抑或往后，进有巅峰可攀，停有风光无限，事业至此刚刚好。湖边，已是风光极致，若得城央叠墅，人生确是刚刚好。<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 0, 0, 0, '', 0, 1, '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `xy_news_data` (`id`, `content`, `readpoint`, `paginationtype`, `maxcharperpage`, `template`, `paytype`, `allow_comment`, `relation`, `copyfrom`, `email`) VALUES
(643, '<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><font face="Times New Roman">常房发<span lang="EN-US">[2011]9</span>号</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="background: white"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><font face="宋体">各县市区房管局、全市各房地产开发企业：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><font face="宋体">现将《预售商品房合同注销及信息变更管理暂行办法》印发给你们，请认真贯彻执行。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p align="center" style="text-align: center; background: white"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><o:p><font face="宋体">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span><font face="宋体"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt">二</span><span style="color: black; font-size: 16pt">〇</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">一一年五月十七日</span></font><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><o:p><font face="宋体">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align="center" style="text-align: center; background: white">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #323e32; font-size: 22pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-width: 90%; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold">预售商品房合同注销及信息变更管理暂行办法</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #323e32; font-size: 22pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-width: 90%; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"> </span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">第一条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>为进一步规范我市商品房销售行为，维护商品房买卖双方当事人合法权益，有效遏制投机性炒房、规避纳税义务的行为，根据《国务院关于坚决遏制部分城市房价过快上涨的通知》、住建部《关于进一步加强房地产市场监管完善商品住房预售制度有关问题的通知》等文件精神，结合我市实际，现就规范商品房预售合同（以下称&ldquo;网签合同&rdquo;）的注销及信息变更行为制定本办法。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">第二条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>常</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥">德市武陵区、常德经济技术开发区、柳叶湖旅游度假区内商品房预售合同的注销及信息变更适用本办法。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">第三条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>进一步增强商品房网签合同严肃性。网签合同应严格执行购房实名制，预购人在签订商品房预售合同后，不得擅自将预购的商品房再行转让。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"> </span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">第四条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>在网上签订了商品房预售合同且进行了备案，符合下列情形的，可进行合同注销或信息变更：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"> </span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">（一）因房地产开发企业工作人员失误，将购房人信息录入错误，需要更正合同信息的<span lang="EN-US">(</span>提交错误内容及更改说明<span lang="EN-US">)</span>；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 31.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">（二）户口本常住人口登记卡索引表中登记的家庭成员之间变更合同买受人信息的<span lang="EN-US">(</span>提交户口本、身份证<span lang="EN-US">)</span>；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 31.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">（三）因房屋质量存在明显问题，经有关部门认定，需解除</font></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">合同的（提交由相关部门出具的质量鉴定报告）；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"> </span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">（四）购房者办理贷款手续未获批准，合同无法继续履行，需要解除合同的（提交不能受理贷款的有效证明）；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 28.2pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">（五）在同一商品房开发项目内调换房屋需注销合同的（提供换购商品房销售合同文本及购房款缴入专户的凭证）；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 28.2pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">（六）经人民法院、仲裁委员会的生效法律文书确认解除网签合同的；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 28.2pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">（七）法律法规规定的其它情形（写明具体内容并提交相关证据）。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"> </span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">第五条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>以下情形不予办理商品房销售合同注销或信息变更手续：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">（一）现售商品房（已在市房管局产权管理处办理了房屋所有权初始登记手续的房屋）销售合同；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">（二）已签订商品房预售合同且已享受政府保障性购房补贴的；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">（三）法律法规规定的其它情形。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">第六条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>申请网签合同注销及信息变更的，按以下程序办理：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 31.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">（一）从常德市房地产信息网下载《常德市商品房预售合同注销（变更）登记备案申请表》，双方如实填写，并签字盖章；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="right" style="text-align: right; text-indent: 31.8pt; margin: 0cm 7pt 0pt 0cm; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><font face="Times New Roman"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">（二）开发企业代表人和买受人携带双方合同原件、身份证明文件及复印件、注销合同理由凭据、《常德市商品房预售合同</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 14pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">&mdash;<span lang="EN-US">3</span>&mdash;<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">注销（变更）登记备案申请表》、公司代表人身份证原件、企业授权委托书等其它相关证明材料，到市房管局办理网签合同注销及信息变更手续。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 31.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">（三）市房管局市场监管科受理申请后进行审查，对符合合同注销（变更）条件的报分管局长批准后在网签系统中注销（变更）网签合同信息。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 31.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">第七条 <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>网签合同中载明两个以上共同购买人的，应提供共同购买人同意注销或变更合同的书面承诺。当事人确实无法到场的，应提交相关证明或公证部门的公证文书。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">第八条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>买受人为法人的，网签合同注销或变更合同信息时应提交有效的法人证书、营业执照以及其它相关证明。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 27.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">第九条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>买受人为未成年人的，应由其监护人代为申请。买受人委托代理人代办的，代理人应提供经公证机关公证的买受人授权委托书。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 27.75pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">第十条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>房地产开发企业对已预售商品房不按国家规定在<span lang="EN-US">30</span>日内办理合同备案手续的，暂停该项目网签手续。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; text-indent: 31.8pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">第十一条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>开发企业应将注销网签合同的房源公开销售，常德市房地产信息网实时公示注销合同的情况。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><font face="Times New Roman"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"> </span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: #323e32; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">第十二条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>本办法自<st1:chsdate year="2011" month="6" w:st="on" day="1" islunardate="False" isrocdate="False"><span lang="EN-US">2011</span>年<span lang="EN-US">6</span>月<span lang="EN-US">1</span>日</st1:chsdate>起实行。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font size="3" face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font size="3" face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family:''Times New Roman''">主题词：</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt">城乡建设　房屋　管理　办法　通知</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><v:line id="_x0000_s1028" to="414pt,.6pt" from="0,.6pt" style="z-index: 251658752; position: absolute; text-align: left; left: 0px"></v:line><font face="宋体"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -1pt; color: black; font-size: 15pt">　</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -1pt; color: black; font-size: 16pt">抄送：省住建厅，市委办，市人大办，市政府办，市政协办。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -1pt; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><font face="宋体">　　　　市住建局，市国土局，市规划局。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 56pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 4.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -1pt; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><font face="宋体">各县市区人民政府，常德经济技术开发区，柳叶湖旅游<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 56pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 4.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -1pt; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><font face="宋体">度假区，西湖、西洞庭管委会。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 16pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0"><v:line id="_x0000_s1027" to="414pt,31.2pt" from="0,31.2pt" style="z-index: 251657728; position: absolute; text-align: left; left: 0px"></v:line><v:line id="_x0000_s1026" to="414pt,0" from="0,0" style="z-index: 251656704; position: absolute; text-align: left; left: 0px"></v:line><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">常德市房地产管理局<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><st1:chsdate year="2011" month="5" w:st="on" day="17" islunardate="False" isrocdate="False">2011<span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">年5</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">月17</span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">日</span></span></st1:chsdate><span lang="EN-US">印发<o:p></o:p></span></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 0, 0, 0, '', 0, 1, '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `xy_news_data` (`id`, `content`, `readpoint`, `paginationtype`, `maxcharperpage`, `template`, `paytype`, `allow_comment`, `relation`, `copyfrom`, `email`) VALUES
(644, '<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt"><font face="Times New Roman">常房发<span lang="EN-US">[2011]8</span>号<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="center" style="text-align: center; background: white"><font face="宋体"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 方正小标宋简体; color: black; font-size: 22pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="background: white"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><font face="宋体">各县市区房管局、全市各房地产开发企业：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><font face="宋体">现将《常德市房开发项目资本金管理暂行办法》印发给你们，请认真贯彻执行。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p align="center" style="text-align: center; background: white"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><o:p><font face="宋体">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align="center" style="text-align: center; background: white"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><o:p><font face="宋体">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align="center" style="text-align: center; background: white"><font face="宋体"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt">二</span><span style="color: black; font-size: 16pt">〇</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312">一一年五月十七日</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p align="center" style="text-align: center; background: white"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><o:p><font face="宋体">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align="center" style="text-align: center; background: white"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><o:p><font face="宋体">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align="center" style="text-align: center; background: white"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><o:p><font face="宋体">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align="center" style="text-align: center; line-height: 28pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><font face="宋体"><span style="color: black; font-size: 22pt">常德市</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 22pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="color: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none"><span lang="EN-US">房</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="color: windowtext; text-decoration: none; text-underline: none"><span lang="EN-US">地产</span></span></span><span style="color: black; font-size: 22pt">开发项目资本金管理暂行办法<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><o:p><font face="宋体">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第一条 <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>为加强房地产开发项目资本金的管理，保障和促进房地产业的健康发展，根据国务院《城市房地产开发经营管理条例》、国务院《关于促进房地产市场持续健康发展的通知》的规定，结合我市实际，制定本办法。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第二条 <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>本办法所称房地产开发项目资本金（以下简称项目资本金），是指在房地产开发项目建设总投资中，由房地产开发企业按规定专户储存，专项用于该房地产开发项目的自有货币资金。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第三条 <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>常德市武陵区、常德经济技术开发区、柳叶湖旅游度假区内国有土地上的房地产开发项目资本金的管理（不含廉租房等保障性住房）适用本办法。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="宋体"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥">第四条 <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>市房管局负责项目资本金的监督管理，同时商请人</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt">民银行和银监局协助做好监督管理工作。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="color: black; font-size: 16pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第五条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>项目资本金的缴存按规划建筑面积计算，标准为：住宅：<span lang="EN-US">100</span>元<span lang="EN-US">/</span>平方米，非住宅：<span lang="EN-US">120</span>元<span lang="EN-US">/</span>平方米。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第六条 <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>开发项目实施分期开发的，项目资本金的缴存可以按规模分期到位。项目的分期规模按市政府常政办发〔<span lang="EN-US">2011</span>〕<span lang="EN-US">20</span>号文件的有关规定办理。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第七条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>项目资本金实行专户管理。房地产开发企业在市房管局指定的金融机构设立项目资本金专用存款帐户，并将受监管的项目资本金按要求全额存入专用帐户。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体"><span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第八条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>开发企业申请开设项目资本金专用存款帐户时，除按照人民银行《银行帐户管理办法》及相关规定要求提供开户申请资料外，还必须向开户的金融机构提供&ldquo;关于接受常德市房地产管理局对开发项目资本金使用监督管理声明&rdquo;（见附件）。开户的金融机构必须将该声明与该帐户预留印鉴共同存放，以备核查。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第九条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>房地产开发企业在项目动工之前依照本办法缴存项目资本金，并持金融机构出具的存款凭证及有关资料，到市房管局办理项目资本金足额缴存的证明后，再到市住房城乡建设局申请领取建筑工程施工许可证。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第十条 <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>项目资本金按项目工程建设进度分三期解控：工程基础（正负零）完成后解控存款总额<span lang="EN-US">20%</span>的资金，工程主体结构完成（封顶）后解控存款总额<span lang="EN-US">30%</span>的资金，工程竣工联合验收合格后解控存款总额<span lang="EN-US">50%</span>的资金。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><font face="宋体"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥">房地产开发企业持加盖&ldquo;常德市房地产开发项目资本金监控管理专用章&rdquo;的取款支票和项目资本金解控通知书办理资金支取手续。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第十一条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>开发企业到市房管局产权管理处办理开发项目的房屋所有权初始登记手续后，方可提出项目资本金账户终止监管申请，经审查批准后，到存款的金融机构办理专用帐户终止监管手续。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第十二条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>开发企业应当将项目资本金的缴存、使用情况记入该项目的《房地产开发项目手册》，项目分期开发的应当分期<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">记录。<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第十三条 <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>项目资本金专用账户管理金融机构工作人员不按本办法规定擅自支付项目资本金的，市房管局将另行指定金融机构进行项目资本金专用账户管理<span lang="EN-US">,</span>造成严重后果的，相关人员承担相应的法律责任。监管部门工作人员在项目资本金的管理工作中玩忽职守、滥用职权、徇私舞弊违反本办法规定的给予行政处分，造成严重后果的，依法追究其法律责任。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第十四条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>开发企业未按本办法规定办理房地产开发项目资本金专户储存手续的由市房管局责令改正<span lang="EN-US">,</span>给予警告<span lang="EN-US">,</span>有非法所得的没收非法所得<span lang="EN-US">,</span>并处<span lang="EN-US">1</span>万元以上<span lang="EN-US">3</span>万元以下的罚款。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第十五条 <span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>鼎城区项目资本金的管理，由鼎城区房管局按照本办法施行。其他县（市）和西湖、西洞庭管理区参照本办法施行。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">第十六条<span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span>本办法自发布之日起施行。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; background: white; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥"><font face="宋体">本办法实施前，已在市住房城乡建设局办理了项目资本金监管手续的，项目资本金的解控，经报市住房城乡建设局审查批准，市房管局盖章后，到存款的金融机构办理资金解控和专用帐户终止监管手续。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 35pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -1pt; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><o:p><font face="宋体">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 35pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; letter-spacing: -1pt; color: black; font-size: 16pt"><font face="宋体">附件：关于接受常德市房地产管理局对开发项目资本金使用监督管理的声明<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体"><font face="Times New Roman">附件<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center; line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 22pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center; line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 22pt">关于接受常德市房地产管理局<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align: center; line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 22pt">对开发项目资本金使用监督管理的声明<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><u><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt"><o:p><span style="text-decoration: none"><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></span></o:p></span></u></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><font face="Times New Roman"><u><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></u><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt">：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0"><font face="Times New Roman"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">根据《常德市房地产开发项目资本金管理暂行办法》的要求，我单位在你行开设的&ldquo;&times;&times;&times;&times;项目资本金专用帐户（账号&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;&times;）&rdquo;，其资金支取必须经过常德市房地产管理局审查、批准，凭加盖&ldquo;</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; color: black; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: ˎ̥">常德市房地产开发项目资本金监控管理专用章</span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt">&rdquo;（见印模）的取款支票和解控通知书，才能支取。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 48pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 3.0"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman">特此声明<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><v:rect id="_x0000_s1026" style="z-index: 251656192; position: absolute; text-align: left; margin-top: 1.6pt; width: 135pt; height: 132.6pt; margin-left: 180pt; left: 0px"></v:rect><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><font face="Times New Roman"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<table border="1" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="1" width="150" align="center" height="150">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <p style="text-align: center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; line-height: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt"><o:p><font face="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="