(764, '<p sizset="false" sizcache04198477190182791="143 98 0"><span sizset="false" sizcache04198477190182791="143 98 0" style="color:#000000;"><span sizset="false" sizcache04198477190182791="143 98 0" style="font-size:16px;"><span sizset="false" sizcache04198477190182791="143 98 0" style="font-family:宋体;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="http://www.0736fdc.com//upfiles/images/201404/031248433574.png" alt="" /></span></span></span></p><p sizset="false" sizcache04198477190182791="143 98 0"><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt;">30</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt;">平米、<span lang="EN-US">40</span>平米、<span lang="EN-US">50</span>平米、<span lang="EN-US">100</span>平米……<span lang="EN-US">1500</span>平米，大小可以任你组合。<span lang="EN-US">7</span>万首付起，租金养贷，小投资者即买即赚。上市公司—大湖股份已进驻办公，大商带动之下，大小企业以及一些创业公司就为在这里争抢一席，公司不动产稳定升值，公司形象直线上升。</span></span><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-family:宋体;"></span></span></span></p><p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt;">星级酒店、咖啡厅、酒庄、餐饮等<span lang="EN-US">2</span>万平米休闲娱乐商业中心火热招商。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt;">泓鑫·桃林位于建设路高山街口——常德百年市中心，堪比任何一城<span lang="EN-US">CBD</span>，寸土寸金。在市中心占地<span lang="EN-US">40</span>亩，建筑规模约<span lang="EN-US">10</span>万㎡，大规模城市综合体。由<span lang="EN-US">4</span>栋央景健康住宅，<span lang="EN-US">1</span>栋<span lang="EN-US">18